@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nrftvc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v2 + 0.97)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp((v0 + 0.96 * v0 + 0.07)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.93) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.96)) / wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.12)))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.96)
    v1 = ((0.75 + (v0 + 0.08 * v2 + 0.21)) + 0.40)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v1 + 0.07 * v1 + 0.68)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp))
    tmp = (v2 - ((v2 + 0.72 * tmp + 0.97) / (v0 + 0.26 * tmp + 0.24)))
    data[tid] = v0
